<h2>Query Tab Properties</h2>
<ol>
	<li>
        <h4>Name</h4>
        A name you can use to identify the query in a list
	</li>
    <li>
        <h4>Connection</h4>
        The connection you want to use when executing this query	
    </li>
    <li>
        <h4>Timeout</h4>
       The timeout for the query execution
    </li>
    <li>
        <h4>SQL</h4>
        SQL that defines the data you wish to return
    </li>
    <li>
        <h4>StoredProc (SQL Only)</h4>
        A Stored Procedure on the database server that you wish to use
    </li>
</ol>
